Our Benefits






Health & Wellness
Calamos is dedicated to helping our associates improve and maintain their health.
Insurance   -  Calamos offers a range of comprehensive coverage options. 
			Eligible associates can enroll in medical, dental, vision, disability and life insurance 
			plans. Health Care, Transportation and Dependent Care Flexible Spending Accounts are 
			also available.
Wellness Events  -  Calamos supports various wellness 
			events from health screenings and flu shots to relaxation and stress management seminars.
Physical Activity  -  Calamos encourages its associates to take 
			advantage of its walking trails and fitness center.
Employee Assistance Program (EAP)  -  All associates are eligible 
			to utilize this counseling and family assistance program at no cost. The EAP offers many resources to help associates and their families 
			overcome life's challenges.







Work Life Balance
Calamos provides solutions to help associates simplify their daily lives such 
			as dry cleaning and car wash services, lactation room and expectant mother 
			parking. Calamos believes in having fun with co-workers outside of work. 
			We support various recreational sports teams like basketball and softball.







Training & Education
Calamos is committed to the professional development of all its associates. 
			The company encourages associates to attend workshops and seminars offered 
			through our in-house curriculum and through external firms.  Calamos also assists 
			associates with the payment of tuition and books for approved educational 
			courses after one year of service with the company.







Paid Time Off
Vacation  -  All full-time associates are eligible for paid vacation.
Sick Days  -  Full-time associates are eligible for up 
			to five sick days per calendar year.
Holiday Schedule  -  Calamos observes the same holiday schedule 
			as the New York Stock Exchange, which typically  includes the following as paid holidays:  
			New Year's Day, Martin Luther King's Birthday, President's Day, Good Friday, 
			Memorial Day, Independence Day, Labor Day, Thanksgiving Day and Christmas Day.







Compensation
Calamos is committed to providing a competitive total rewards package that 
			allows us to attract and retain talented associates. Our success depends on the expertise 
			of our associates and their ability to work together as an effective team.







Retirement Savings
The Calamos Profit Sharing 401(k) Plan is designed to help associates achieve 
			financial security for their retirement.  The plan includes the following components.
401(k) - Calamos offers associates the option to contribute 
			to traditional before tax 401(k) and Roth 401(k).
Company Match - The plan has a 50% match on deferrals of up to 
			6% of total compensation, or a maximum company contribution of 3% of total compensation.
Profit Sharing - Calamos associates are eligible for annual 
			discretionary profit sharing contributions.




Why Calamos?

Company Cafeteria
Calamos encourages associates to eat together.  Our gourmet cafeteria offers daily entrees, 
	salad bar, sandwich station, make-your-own pizza and more.

Calamos' Green Building
The 180,000 square foot office building is a first-class, state-of-the-art headquarters. 
	One of the first privately developed buildings in Chicago registered under 
	LEED Green Building Rating System. 
	Read more »








