Life @ Calamos

Calamos offers an entrepreneurial environment where employees can collaborate with 
	some of the industry's most extraordinary individuals. Calamos takes pride in our 
	integrity, professionalism and relentless focus on putting our clients first. At 
	Calamos we are passionate about what we do and are committed to excellence.
Growing your Career at Calamos
Calamos places a high priority on the development of its associates. 
	We provide quality learning opportunities to support the development of associates 
	and the achievement of the strategic goals and values of the firm. At Calamos we 
	strive to expand associate's skill set expertise, develop leadership and an 
	execution-driven culture and support continuous learning and the sharing of 
	knowledge across the organization.
Calamos Academy
The Calamos Academy is a strategic commitment to the long-term success 
	of the company and its associates. It supports the mission of making Calamos 
	a learning organization with a focus on excellent client service and continuous 
	improvement.
Calamos Academy provides a multitude of resources for the development 
	of Calamos associates including instructor-led and eLearning courses as well 
	as educational whitepapers, videos, etc.  Calamos Academy includes not only a 
	physical training center but also an online learning portal for Associates – 
	The Calamos Academy Virtual Campus. This online platform provides learning 
	resources to assist associates with the development of their skills and 
	knowledge of the industry, investments fundamentals, business skills, 
	leadership development and more.
Community Involvement and Sponsored Events






Calamos Cares
Calamos Cares is the company's community volunteering program, which provides opportunities for associates to share their time and talents with local and national non-profit organizations. The program also allows associates to create stronger relationships with each other outside of the workplace. The Calamos Cares team has volunteered at the Northern Illinois Food Bank and participated in both the March of Dimes March for Babies and the American Cancer Society Relay for Life.








Take Our Daughters and Sons to Work Day
Calamos participates in the annual Take Our Daughters and Sons to Work Day, which helps bring 
			children into the workplace to understand their parents' daily activities, as well as 
			explore personal career choices.








Naperville Wine Festival
Calamos is the host and one of the lead sponsors of the annual Naperville Wine Festival, held in August at CityGate Centre. A portion of the proceeds from the Naperville Wine Festival are donated to the Naperville Area Humane Society and Alex's Lemonade Stand Foundation.
			








Naperville Area Chamber of Commerce
Calamos has been a member of the Naperville Area Chamber of Commerce since 1994. 
			The company sponsors the Chamber's annual Economic Forecast Breakfast and the 
			organization's Inaugural Gala where past board members are thanked for their 
			service to the community and current board members are introduced, 
			including a representative from Calamos.








Choose DuPage
Calamos is a leader in regional economic development through Choose DuPage, 
			an organization that drives economic development in DuPage County by leveraging the 
			area's growth for the benefit of county businesses and residents. John Calamos, Sr. 
			is on the board of directors for the organization.




Why Calamos

Company Cafeteria
Calamos encourages associates to eat together.  Our gourmet cafeteria offers daily entrees, 
	salad bar, sandwich station, make-your-own pizza and more.

“Best Places to Live”
2016 Money Magazine rated Naperville, IL as a Best Place to Live because of great job 
	opportunities, top-notch schools, safe streets, economic strength and more. To learn more 
	about Naperville visit: Naperville.net

Calamos' Green Building
The 180,000 square foot office building is a first-class, state-of-the-art headquarters. 
	One of the first privately developed buildings in Chicago registered under LEED Green 
	Building Rating System. 
	
