Calamos Global Funds plc Announces Dividend, Payable on June 8, 2016
Jun 2 16
Calamos Global Funds Plc announced a dividend of EUR 0.03203 per share on Class A EUR Distributing shares, GBP 0.03328 per share on Class A GBP Distributing shares, USD 0.04055 per share on Class A USD Distributing shares, EUR 0.03598 per share on Class I EUR Distributing shares, GBP 0.03596 per share on Class I GBP Distributing shares, USD 0.03581 per share on Class I USD Distributing shares, CHF 0.03650 per share on Class Z CHF Distributing shares, GBP 0.03643 per share on Class Z GBP Distributing shares, and EUR 0.02801 per share on Class Z EUR Distributing shares. The dividend will be payable on June 8, 2016 with the record date of May 27, 2016.


