            Calamos Holdings is a publicly held company that offers a range of financial services and products through its subsidiaries. The company operates Calamos Advisors LLC, which is an investment advisory firm. Its Calamos Family Partners is a privately held company. Calamos Holdings offers a range of open-end mutual funds through its subsidiary, Calamos Financial Services. Its subsidiaries also provide asset allocation and investment and wealth management solutions. The company serves high-net-worth individuals, institutions, family offices and foundations. In operation for more than 25 years, the company offers equity, balanced, convertible, high-yield, alternative, fixed-income and money market investment products. Calamos Holdings additionally operates Calamos Property Management and Calamos Wealth Management.
          






















